LJava
Interface Lazy<P>

Type Parameters:
P - - The type of returned type from the lazy evaluation (prevents you from later casting).
All Known Implementing Classes:
Constraint
public interface Lazy<P>

Author:
Tzali Maimon This interface allows you to use several features of LJ through lazy evaluation.

for more details you should read more at logicjava.wordpress.com
